We construct the spherically symmetric, steady solution of the NDW using parameter set in the first line of Table \ref{tab:modelpar}.
They are parameters of the HN wind used in \cite{2015ApJ...810..115F}.
Then, we perform the nucleosynthesis calculation on the constructed wind solution.
Now we include the (anti)neutrino-absorption reactions of nucleons.
