The $\alpha$QSE abundance minimizes the free energy (i.e., Equation \ref{eq1}) under the constraints of Equations (\ref{eq3})-(\ref{eq5}).
We obtain such an abundance using the method of Lagrange multiplier.
We find the abundance for that the function

